@startuml pcard-paperboy-proposed
title P-Card Management - Proposed Paperboy Workflow

skinparam activityBackgroundColor #F0FFF0
skinparam activityBorderColor #46B446

|Employee|
start
:Submit P-Card request\nvia Paperboy form;

|Supervisor|
:Receive notification;
:Approve / deny in Paperboy;

|Bill Responsible Party|
:Receive notification;
:Approve / deny in Paperboy;

|Department Head|
:Receive notification;
:Approve / deny in Paperboy;

|Procurement Services|
:Geraldine or Julie Miller
receives approved request;
:Order card;
:Mark training required;

|Employee|
repeat
  :Take training exam;
repeat while (Pass?) is (no) not (yes)

|Procurement Services|
:Record training completion;
:Notify employee - card ready;

|Employee|
:Pick up card;

|Procurement Services|
:P-Card inventory auto-updated;
stop

note right
  **Replaces annual audit:**
  - Inventory stays current in real-time
  - Admin council can review/modify
    cardholder list at any time
  - No more annual email audit cycle
end note

@enduml
